  "short_text": "Smallest Number in the List - 2",
  "content": "Write a program to print the smallest number in the list.<hr><b>Input</b><br/><br/>The input will be a single line containing the comma-separated integers.<hr><b>Output</b><br/><br/>The output should be a single line containing the smallest number in the list.<hr><b>Explanation</b><br/><br/>For example, if the given string is &quot;2,4,-1,5&quot;, your code should print the smallest number in the list. So the output should be -1.",
